- [ ] TypeScript strict mode
- [ ] Implement keyboard navigation
- [ ] Add ARIA labels
- [ ] Support dark mode

**Before Completion:**
- [ ] Write unit tests
- [ ] Lazy load heavy components
- [ ] Check bundle size: `npm run build`
- [ ] Review with code-reviewer skill

